<taxonomicName id="4C1235C26105FFF0FF23F88F7704C034" authority="Martinez and D'Andretta" authorityName="Martinez and D'Andretta" box="[192,820,1859,1883]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Paulosawaya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ornatissima">
<emphasis id="B96692536105FFF0FF23F88F75CAC034" box="[192,506,1859,1883]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Paulosawaya ornatissima</emphasis>
Martínez and D’Andretta
</taxonomicName>
, by original designation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3081DCA610AFFFFFF23FF0A7058C611" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BAD4E41610AFFFFFF23FF0A7058C611" blockId="24.[192,1440,198,383]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFF23FF0A7507C7B1" bold="true" box="[192,311,198,222]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Remark.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFE28FF0A7640C7B1" box="[459,624,198,222]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Paulosawaya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFE28FF0A7640C7B1" box="[459,624,198,222]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Paulosawaya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was originally placed in the tribe 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFBC7FF0A70F6C7B1" authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" box="[1060,1222,198,222]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Pachydemini">Pachydemini</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8333B0610AFFFFFB15FF0A75AFC791" author="Martinez, A. &amp; M. A. V. D'Andretta" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="345 - 356" refId="ref18871" refString="Martinez, A., and M. A. V. D'Andretta. 1956. Dos generos e especies novos de Pachydemini do Equador (Col. Scarabaeoidea, Melolonthidae). Papeis Avulsos do Departamento de Zoologia 12 (17): 345 - 356." type="journal article" year="1956">Martínez and D’Andretta (1956)</bibRefCitation>
. Later it was transferred to the tribe 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFCBAFF2A70ECC791" authority="(Martinez 1975)" baseAuthorityName="Martinez" baseAuthorityYear="1975" box="[857,1244,230,254]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Macrodactylini">
Macrodactylini (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8333B0610AFFFFFBFCFF2A70E4C791" author="Martinez, A." box="[1055,1236,230,254]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="227 - 251" refId="ref18836" refString="Martinez, A. 1975. Contribucion al conocimiento de los Pachydemini neotropicales (Col. Scarabaeidae, Melolonthinae). Entomologischen Arbeiten aus dem Museum G. Frey 26: 227 - 251." type="journal article" year="1975">Martínez 1975</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, but was considered 
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFF1EFECB7594C671" box="[253,420,262,286]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">incertae sedis</emphasis>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8333B0610AFFFFFE32FECA76A9C671" author="Katovich, K." box="[465,665,262,286]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="1 - 78" refId="ref18612" refString="Katovich, K. 2008. A generic-level phylogenetic review of the Macrodactylini (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Melolonthinae). Insecta Mundi 23: 1 - 78." type="journal article" year="2008">Katovich (2008)</bibRefCitation>
. When I examined 
<specimenCount id="9D1485C8610AFFFFFC66FECA700BC670" box="[901,1083,262,287]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" type="generic" typeStatus="paratypes">four paratypes</specimenCount>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFB83FECA7190C671" box="[1120,1440,262,286]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Paulosawaya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ornatissima">
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFB83FECA7190C671" box="[1120,1440,262,286]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Paulosawaya ornatissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the HAHC, it was immediately obvious that this species belongs in the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFB51FEEA7179C651" box="[1202,1353,294,318]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Clavipalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFB51FEEA7179C651" box="[1202,1353,294,318]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Clavipalpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. These specimens match the latest definition of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFCC6FE8A778AC631" box="[805,954,326,350]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Clavipalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFCC6FE8A778AC631" box="[805,954,326,350]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Clavipalpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8333B0610AFFFFFC00FE8A7098C631" author="Katovich, K." box="[995,1192,326,350]" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" pagination="1 - 78" refId="ref18612" refString="Katovich, K. 2008. A generic-level phylogenetic review of the Macrodactylini (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Melolonthinae). Insecta Mundi 23: 1 - 78." type="journal article" year="2008">Katovich (2008)</bibRefCitation>
. The transfer is here made, placing the generic name 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFDA6FEAA76D8C611" box="[581,744,358,382]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Paulosawaya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFDA6FEAA76D8C611" box="[581,744,358,382]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Paulosawaya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="4C1235C2610AFFFFFC2FFEAA7051C611" box="[972,1121,358,382]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Clavipalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9669253610AFFFFFC2FFEAA7051C611" box="[972,1121,358,382]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="23">Clavipalpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
